DTC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 個月前\",\"text\":\"不錯吃👍🏻 日式定食牛肉奶油燒黑胡椒微辣\\n很下飯～～～\\n杏鮑菇小菜還有加芥末口感很協調好吃😋\\n\\n壽司🍣 口感也不錯😀 煙燻鮭魚捲🤩\",\"time\":1743934835,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Lee lee\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106362108521048371504/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUb0Xch0Su3UdZaZUiWvQDDggchnA6p5j5B6AYknCHUna_-jrQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 個月前\",\"text\":\"鮭魚頭火鍋很不錯，可惜不喜歡魚頭先油炸過。天婦蘿定食，炸金針菇、炸紅蘿蔔？不知道那團是什麼，炸得太油膩了，滿嘴是油。鯖魚定食很不錯，肉質肥美。整體都還不錯\",\"time\":1741595211,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Li Tzu Wang\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109219011406387629032/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKTBTXwiyaUBXdgrYbeb-tJzYGatAvtY_OY1XWtTvTBMQyrUc6aw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"6 個月前\",\"text\":\"海景刺生定食生魚片很多種，沒有腥味～讚\\n配上紫蘇也很好吃！蒸蛋有小蝦仁，整份定食還不錯，不過菜比較少。最後的甜點不會很甜，老少咸宜，適合當作一餐的ending👍\\n定食的飯跟湯都可以續呦！\\n\\n炒高麗菜很好吃～份量不少\\n\\n五仔魚中規中矩\\n\\n綜合壽司蠻多種的，上面的生魚片就像海景定食那樣\\n\\n服務生感覺都做很久了，態度都很客氣，也會積極加水，詢問湯飯有無需要續\\n\\n整體來說還可以，而且有自己的停車場，座位也很多～\\n\\n可惜的是若在尖峰時段，客人很多的時候，廁所會不夠，因為男女廁只有各一間，更何況員工也需要上，這樣偏不方便😢\",\"time\":1733282670,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNQ4sk_igTsaXIDfFnEXOFNo5IcHG-H790Dl8YVkbLjI06F4KTyKiXEGSCZLWN9cOuyxYFx5QCg8cBHuQfVJdTEmyPewWdgboGx1HdAOovktYAAJoUF_Q6x7zZ0ZLa4Y9egSAftdflCdS6JaolQ7jtKmLp31kyla5pm1fGbPEErWDWGxmcaZUeU0gXz1hEvWUgk4ujv_WqWwNC7Z1QdawnHlrisOgJS6CvFUJu6QR-S3C9NISqaAeF8T_5Tbvq4HO0ttD2bCZTYn6iZe-sNLndGooJ-pKEqJ_XiySeFkq-B3DzFzpvqIFFZlMHyALKWAmlrPR7pxvoBPOzPMYwij-cePrDyGNgCDqz3GlHIOVVxh3OAerRF7eoW9iHakMASOhiW2p5YV2ViHQyMAgo0xS2EDKo-or-xhHgPDiqBgXnkCx9W7UX4hZ9xNvQX1UEwGI-qg4R2DjZtZtWmRqL-azljMMKbvAmQVOrF28QOW7yUh7x_vJNpdDegyrckMp-t7Kb1FyND7-Sd9tywXFBAQZHXTjI7b_gDxB5OmtH2EjbbjXP9lbMbe7oUR9t5s8xZg6-vClkEG3l_hvY5EdwmTvnW